      "text": "House Republicans mourn the loss of Congressman Doug LaMalfa.\n\nA lifelong resident of Northern California and a fourth-generation rice farmer, Congressman LaMalfa spent more than two decades in public service. He proudly represented California’s 1st Congressional District from 2013 to 2026, serving as Chairman of the Congressional Western Caucus.\n\nPlease join us in praying for Congressman LaMalfa’s wife, kids, and staff.",
